		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/rt-artile-about-mi6s-afghan-ghost-money.html" title="Permalink to RT article about MI6’s Afghan “ghost money”" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> article about <span class="caps">MI6</span>’s Afghan “ghost money”</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/rt-artile-about-mi6s-afghan-ghost-money.html" title="14:39" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-05-07T14:39:16+00:00" pubdate>May 7, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/rt-artile-about-mi6s-afghan-ghost-money.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here’s a <a href="http://rt.com/op-edge/mi6-cia-tax-money-drugs-941/">link to my new art­icle</a>, pub­lished exclus­ively today on <a href="http://rt.com/op-edge/"><span class="caps">RT</span>’s Op-Edge</a> news site.</p>
<p>I dis­cuss the recent news that <span class="caps">MI6</span>, in addi­tion to the <span class="caps">CIA</span>, has been pay­ing “ghost money” to the polit­ical estab­lish­ment in Afgh­anistan, other examples of such med­dling, and the prob­able unin­ten­ded consequences.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
