				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/accountability-2" rel="tag">accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gaddafi" rel="tag">Gaddafi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gibson" rel="tag">Gibson</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/isc" rel="tag">ISC</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi6" rel="tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/rifkind" rel="tag">Rifkind</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>			</span>
						
